{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/NoWaitHero_Gif1.gif?t=1588921040\" /><br>Deck building card battle &quot;NoWaitHero&quot;<br>There is no need to wait during a duel.<br>Seize the victory ahead of the choice.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/NoWaitHero_Gif2.gif?t=1588921040\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In this game, you don't have to wait for the enemy to act.<br>They act at the same time as each other. There is no need to wait for the other party.<br>The enemy's movements are predictable, so let's get ahead of them.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/NoWaitHero_Gif3.gif?t=1588921040\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can get new cards by defeating enemies.<br>Cards are stacked and only the top card can be used.<br>The choice you make will make a big difference in the battle.\u3000<br>Build up your cards and experience to take on more formidable enemies.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/extras/NoWaitHero_Gif4.gif?t=1588921040\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The card has restrictions on use.<br>If you use it crudely, you'll be pushed into a corner.<br>The enemy is also a hero.<br>Use it all to your advantage and win in style!</li></ul><br>You are the one who will defeat all the heroes and win the Hero Royal.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1588921040","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1588921040","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289900/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1588921040","capsule_imagev5":"https://shar